{
  "texts": [
    "We provided a thorough overview of Deep Learning architectures and reviewed the applications of CNN in medical imaging.",
    "It was observed that Deep Learning techniques based on CNNs are becoming more widely accepted in all areas of early disease detection including DR, lung cancer, AD, etc.",
    "Data augmentation and transfer learning are examples of methods used to solve problems with Deep Learning methods caused by inadequate data and labels.",
    "Improved Deep Learning architectures and much more computation power are making it possible to function better on massive datasets.",
    "This achievement could eventually lead to enhanced computer-assisted detection and treatment systems."
  ]
}